When we create a Service desk, the permission scheme is created automatically .And in this permission scheme for all possible actions like Browse Project, Create issue, Development Tools, Close issue, Edit issue ,  "Application Role (Any logged in user)" is added 

This is a Defect. As it opens up my Project Specific service desk to everyone who is added as a user in JIRA. This is a security breach.

